attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a table. He starts by inspecting the legs, shelf, and table. Then, he uses an allen wrench to screw in the first screw. He continues screwing in screws, rotating the table clockwise, and assembling the legs until all the screws are in. Finally, he uses a screwdriver to tighten all the screws.
